title: The Happy Camel Pita Bakery and Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Middle Eastern
description: Deli style primarily take-out with a lunch counter for seating. Offers hot lunches from soup and salads to pizza and baked falafel in a pita. Makes vegan pita bread, which includes organic whole wheat pita, in addition to vegetarian Mediterranean dips and spreads. Has gluten free.
